{"tid":1108253,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"女魔頭 Angela Ahrendts 今日正式離開蘋果","createTime":"2019-04-15T23:19:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T15:46:41.000Z","uid":6848,"like":63,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e4786145492a44c80186640938055a8440e19cc6","tid":1108253,"uid":6848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T23:19:26.000Z","msg":"在今年 2 月的監管文件中，蘋果宣佈零售主管 Angela Ahrendts 將於美國時間 4 月 15 日，也就是今天離開蘋果。蘋果新任零售主管是 Deirdre O&rsquo;Brien，O&rsquo;Brien 之前的職位是人員副總裁，新職位是零售和人員高級副總裁。除了管理人員，O&rsquo;Brien 還將負責蘋果零售業務。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEkgc8E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEkgc8E.png&h=12f5006c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在上週末，蘋果已經將 Angela Ahrendts 的名字從高管頁面移除，為她的離開做好準備。根據蘋果，Angela Ahrendts 因為個人和專業追求而離開蘋果，目前還不清楚 Angela Ahrendts 離開蘋果之後的計劃。蘋果也沒有深度解釋 Angela Ahrendts 為什麼會離開，但有分析人士推測，Angela Ahrendts 的離開與 iPhone 在中國銷量下滑有關係。<br />\n<br />\nAngela Ahrendts 2014 年加入蘋果，一直擔任蘋果零售主管。在 Angela Ahrendts 的領導下，蘋果將原來的天才吧設計為 Genius Grove，減少第三方配件銷售，並將零售店升級為社區中心，推出了 Today at Apple 等活動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.macx.cn/forum/201904/16/020208l2lxrxj4xzj4tt85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.macx.cn%2Fforum%2F201904%2F16%2F020208l2lxrxj4xzj4tt85.jpg&h=11062ce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加入蘋果之前，Angela Ahrendts 是巴寶莉的 CEO。Angela Ahrendts 加入蘋果時，蘋果想要將數碼產品當成奢侈品賣，比如 2015 年發佈的 14K 金  Apple Watch Edition。那麼問題來了，Angela Ahrendts 離開之後，未來的蘋果產品價格會降下來嗎？<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.macx.cn/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=2221993&amp;extra=&amp;ordertype=2&amp;threads=thread\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.macx.cn%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D2221993%26extra%3D%26ordertype%3D2%26threads%3Dthread&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCd9qeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=0bb50beb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.macx.cn/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=2221993&amp;extra=&amp;ordertype=2&amp;threads=thread</a>"},{"pid":"a79cf545ffc1f15da1177c8a6b2d9100969d90f6","tid":1108253,"uid":118647,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T23:46:43.000Z","msg":"我覺得個價唔會降，但應該維持一段時間"},{"pid":"2ee3ea419b99f9a2a12c62407a59bc0d46572922","tid":1108253,"uid":168366,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:26:34.000Z","msg":"係覺得佢Today at Apple同Apple Store的look比較更無科技嗰種冷冰感warm d搞得好<br />\n<br />\n其他就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650d12647aedb3a1fd66e52f533e78147fa2dbb3","tid":1108253,"uid":19789,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"2ee3ea419b99f9a2a12c62407a59bc0d46572922","tid":1108253,"uid":168366,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:26:34.000Z","msg":"係覺得佢Today at Apple同Apple Store的look比較更無科技嗰種冷冰感warm d搞得好<br />\n<br />\n其他就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:28:27.000Z","msg":"平心而論佢retail store嗰part係做到親民感嘅<br />\n不過啲產品價錢就一啲都唔親民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeab37a31a59e561ca4fbe6712989c54bf686410","tid":1108253,"uid":112416,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:32:46.000Z","msg":"上次出新iPhone嗰陣，個個連登仔都話一萬蚊唔係乜野錢，而家就個個都想呢個女人消失"},{"pid":"77709b5220019cd17fdb33b5fa3349491e8a0053","tid":1108253,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:34:23.000Z","msg":"個價賣到咁高連大陸人傻錢多都唔埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888c4a14c95bdc9a9cfd92e8c909d20f5dd94733","tid":1108253,"uid":19789,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eeab37a31a59e561ca4fbe6712989c54bf686410","tid":1108253,"uid":112416,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T02:32:46.000Z","msg":"上次出新iPhone嗰陣，個個連登仔都話一萬蚊唔係乜野錢，而家就個個都想呢個女人消失"},